quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  46,1,"Haa, Miim"
  46,2,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  46,3,"Men tagiraali kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, si wanaa e goonga e lajala happaangal [fii mun]. YedduЙ“e Й“en ko Й—uurniiЙ“e e ko Й“e rentiniraa kon"
  46,4,"Maaku: \"On yi'ii ko rewoton kon hara wanaa Allah, hollee lam ko Й—i tagi e leydi ndin? Kaa hara hiЙ—i mari geЙ“al e [tagugol] kammuuli Й—in? Awa addanee lam Deftere jippinaande ado ndee Й—oo maaЙ—um batte ganndal, si wonii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  46,5,"Ko hommbo Й“uri majjude, wa on rewoowo ko wanaa Allah, kon ko jaabotaako mo haa Г‘alnde Darngal? Hara Й—in [reweteeЙ—i] ko welsindiiЙ—i e dewal majji"
  46,6,"Si yimЙ“e Й“en mooЙ“oyaama [ka Darngal], Й—i wontanoyay Й“e ayЙ“e, Й“e wona e yeddugol ko Й“e rewaynooЙ—i kon"
  46,7,"Si Aayeeje Amen Й“annguЙ—e Й—en janngaama e maЙ“Й“e, yedunooЙ“e goonga Й“en tuma nde arnoo e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wi'a: \"ЖҠum ko mbilewu Й“anngu ngu"
  46,8,"Kaa Й“e wi'ay woni :\"O fefindi nde?\" Awa maaku: \"Si taw mi fefindi nde, awa doo on duncantaa lam huunde e [lepte] Allah Й—en. Ko Kanko Й“uri anndude on, tuma nde jumpoton e mayre. O yonii seedee hakkunde am e mon. Ko Kanko woni Haforowo, HinnotooЙ—o On"
  46,9,"Maaku: \"Mi wonaa arano e NulaaЙ“e Й“en; mi anndaa kadi ko waЙ—etee mi, maa ko waЙ—eteЙ—on. Mi jokkaa si wanaa ko wahayinaa kon e am; mi laataaki si wanaa jertinoowo Й“anngina"
  46,10,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, si tawii le konde iwrunde ka Allah, yedduЙ—on Й—um, seedotooЙ—o e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'ila Й“en seedii e [sellugol] Й—um, o gomЙ—ini, onon kan townitiЙ—on...Pellet, Allah fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  46,11,"YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'ani gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en: \"Si tawno Й—um ko moЖҙЖҙere, Й“en (waasuЙ“e) adototaako men e mun\". Nde wonunoo Й“e fewnoraali nde, ma Й“e wi'u: \"Ndee ko fenaande neeЙ“unde"
  46,12,"Hino aditiinde, Deftere Muusaa nden, Й—owornde e yurmeende. Ndee Й—oo kadi, ko Deftere goonginir- nde [Й—eya Defte] e Й—emngal aarabu, fii yo jertinir (nde) tooГұooЙ“e Й“en e wewlinirnde moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  46,13,"Pellet, wi'uЙ“e Й“en: \"Ko Allah woni Joomi amen\", refti Й“e tabiti (e gomЙ—inal), kulol alanaa Й“en, wanaa kamЙ“e sunoytoo"
  46,14,"Ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en duumotooЙ“e ton, njoЙ“di ko Й“e gollaynoo kon"
  46,15,"Men yamirii neЙ—Й—anke on moЖҙЖҙagol e jibimЙ“e mo Й“en: Jiido makko soworike mo saЙ—teende, o jibiniri mo kadi saЙ—teende; soweede mo e enteede mo ko lebbi cappanЙ—e tati, haa ka o si o yottike sagatalaaku makku ngun o timminii duuЙ“i cappanЙ—e nayi, o wi'a: \"Joomi, longinam yettugol neema Ma mo neeminirЙ—aa mi min e jibimЙ“e lam, e nde mi gollata moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i weltinayЙ—e Ma, moЖҙЖҙinanaa lam geyngol am ngol. Mi tuubanii Ma, ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en"
  46,16,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Men jaЙ“anta ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e golli, Men yawtana Й“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e, (Й“e jeyaama) e yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en. ЖҠum ko fodoore goonga nde Й“e fodanoo"
  46,17,"Kala non wi'anЙ—o jibimЙ“e mo Й“en: \"Uf mo'on ! Kere on foday lam immintineede hara le gomЙ—ii mofte yawtiino ado lam?\" Hara Й“en Й—iЙ—o no faabtinora Allah [wiide mo]: \"Ee bone maa, GomЙ—in ! Pellet, fodooree Allah nde ko goonga\". O wi'a: \"ЖҠum wonaali, si wanaa tinndi adinooЙ“e Й“en"
  46,18,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Konngol ngol jojji e mun, (Й“e jeyaama) e mofte yawtunooЙ—e ado maЙ“Й“e, immorde e jinna e yimЙ“e. Pellet, Й“e laatino sooyuЙ“e"
  46,19,"Hino woodani kala [fedde e maЙ“Й“e]: darjaaji e ko Й“e golli kon, fii no O hunnirana Й“e njoЙ“di golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en; e hoore Й“e tooГұetaake"
  46,20,"Г‘alnde heeferЙ“e Й“en weeЙ“itoytee e Yiite ngen (Й“e wi'anee): \"On naЙ“ii moЖҙЖҙi mon Й—in ka nguurndam mon aduna, dakmitorЙ—on Й—i. Hannde non, on yoЙ“itirte lepte hoynooje, sabu ko townitoraynoЙ—on kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko huuwiraynoЙ—on kon faasiqaaku"
  46,21,"Janto fii musiЙ—Й“e Aadi (Huudi) Й“en, nde o jertinirnoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en aynde nden - gomЙ—ii hari jertinooji yawtiino yeeso makko e Й“aawo makko - wonnde: \"Wata on rewu si wanaa Allah. Min miЙ—o hulani on lepte Гұalaande mawnde"
  46,22,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"E a aru men fii yo a firliaa men e rewetee- Й—i amen Й—in? Awa addan men ko kammbiranЙ—aa men kon, si wonii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  46,23,"O maaki: \"Ganndal ngal ko ka Allah woni. Min mi yottinanay on tun woni, ko mi nulaa kon. Ko woni tun mi yi'ii ko on yimЙ“e majjaaЙ“e"
  46,24,"Nde Й“e yi'unoo ruulde honde weeЙ“itii fewtiri ayЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e wi'i: \"Ndee ko duulere toЙ“aynde e men\". Ko nden kan woni ! ko hawjirnoЙ—on kon : ko henndu, ndu lepte muusuЙ—e woni e mun"
  46,25,"hindu muncira kala huunde, yamiroore Joomi mayru\". ЖҒe waЙ—tini, tawi yi'etaake si wanaa koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“itirta yimЙ“e bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  46,26,"GomЙ—ii Men yeЙ—iino Й“e, e kon ko Men yeЙ—aali on e mun. Men waЙ—ani Й“e nanЙ—e, e giiЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e. Kono Й—en nanЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, e giiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e (fow) duncanaali Й“e goЙ—Й—um, tawde Й“e laatino yeddooЙ“e Aayeeje Allah Й—en. Ko Й“e jalkitaynoo kon jippii e maЙ“Й“e"
  46,27,"GomЙ—ii Men halkiino ca'e wonunooЙ“e sera mon; Men firlitiri Aayeeje Й—en, belajo'o Й“e ruttoto"
  46,28,"Ko haЙ—no Й—in Й—i Й“e jogitornoo reweteeЙ—i Й“aЙ—tinorЙ—i gaanin Allah, faaboo Й“e? Tigi on, Й—in majjirii Й“e; ko Й—um wonunoo fenaande maЙ“Й“e e ko Й“e fefindotonoo"
  46,29,"Janto tuma nde Men imminnoo fedde jinna e maaЙ—a, hiЙ—i heЙ—oo Alqur'aana. Nde Й—i tawanoo Й—um, Й—i wi'i: \"HeЙ—ee\"...Nde [janngin kin] timmunoo, Й—i huccitiri ka yimЙ“e majji, jeertinooji"
  46,30,"ЖҠi wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu amen, men nanii Deftere jippinaande Й“aawo Muusaa, goonginnde Й—en adiiЙ—e nde. Hinde fewna e goonga e laawol focciingol"
  46,31,"Ko ono yo mbatu amen, nootee noddoowo e Allah on, gomЙ—inon mo. [Ontuma] O haforanay on junuubimon Й—in, O daЙ—nda on lepte muusuЙ—e"
  46,32,"Kala mo nootaake noddoowo e Allah on, o wonaa laawotooЙ—o ka leydi, o alaa kadi giЙ—o gaanin Makko. Ko Й“en woni e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  46,33,"E Й“ee yi'aali wonnde ko Allah tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, O ronkiraali tagugol Й—i, wonnde ko O haЙ—tanЙ—o wuurnitugol maayЙ“e Й“en? Ko non woniri. Pellet, ko O haЙ—tanЙ—o kala huunde"
  46,34,"Г‘alnde heeferЙ“e Й“en weeЙ“itoytee e Yiite ngen, [Й“e wi'anee]: \"Wanaa goonga nii?\" ЖҒe wi'a : \"Ko non woniri! Men woondirii Joomi amen!\". O Daala : \"Awa meeЙ—iree non lepte Й—en, sabu kon ko yeddiraynoЙ—on"
  46,35,"MuГұГұor muГұal joomiraaЙ“e pellital Й“en ka NulaaЙ“e; wata a hawjan Й“e. Г‘alnde Й“e yi'oyta ko Й“e kammbiranaa kon, Й“e wa'oyay wa si Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano [ka leydi] si wanaa dumunna-hun Гұalorma. ЖҠun ko yottinal. Ko homЙ“e halketee si wanaa yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"